name: Anis (NIKKE)
description:
Nikke's Anise Lora

Now version 2

Increased trigger word and capacity for more fidelity.

clothes and hair ornaments have improved, but they are still incomplete.

recommended weight : 0.8

trigger word : anis, anisornament, anisclothing

The preview image uses AOM2Hard, anything4.0, 7thanime

Not sure about other models as I have not used them

modelVersions.description:
I made it for the first time, so it may not be output well

Weight 0.8 may be good

Trigger words : anis

I tested it with some models (AOM2, anything4.5, 7thanime) and output well.

The problem is that the shape of the hair ornament is strange.

This is a future task, and I will fix it.

I'm posting in detail in real time on Twitter, so please.

twitter
